rows.label: tlk4330014501_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey again! My curiosity got the better
of me, so I went over to the Great
Stairway myself to see what was up.

rows.label: tlk4330014501_msg0002
rows.name:
I found that Superbian, but he
was all beat up on the ground!
So I took him to a doctor.

rows.label: tlk4330014501_msg0003
rows.name:
No need to thank me. I wouldn't leave
anyone high and dry like that, not even
an Superbian.
